{
  "info": {
    "name": "Job Portal Backend API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Job Portal Backend - a NestJS-based Job Seeking & Hiring Platform.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Create an environment with `baseUrl` (e.g. http://localhost:3000) and optionally `token`\n3. Run **Auth > Login** first to get an access token\n4. The collection uses `{{token}}` for protected routes - set it manually or use a script to save from Login response\n\n## Authentication\n- **Public routes**: Auth Login\n- **Protected routes**: All others require `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`\n\n## Roles\n- **admin**: Full access\n- **job_seeker**: Jobs (view), Applications (view/create), Profiles (own)\n- **employer**: Companies, Jobs (create/edit), Applications (manage own jobs), Profiles (own)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "companyId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "jobId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "applicationId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "conversationId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "roleId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201 || pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.access_token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.access_token);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login with username and password. Returns `access_token` (JWT).\n\n**Default seeded user:** admin / 1234\n\nResponse: `{ \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGc...\" }`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Logout. Client should discard the token. Server returns a message."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Authentication endpoints. Login is public; Logout requires Bearer token."
    },
    {
